data.description: Adorable and turn key ready, this lovely home is ready to go!  Bright kitchen with lots of cabinets and convenient first floor laundry area.  Formal dining / living room centrally located.  First floor also features two bedrooms (one currently being used as living room) and quaint enclosed front porch.  Full bath and additional bedroom upstairs with large closet.  Attached garage and lovely back yard make this the perfect house for just starting out or looking to downsize.  Fast closing possible, call today for your private viewing.
